name: Diego
bio: Diego is a 2.5 year old cat who is so handsome! He was found as a stray and is all fixed up and ready for a home! He is a little shy but absolutely loves to be held and cuddled! And he will give you love back! Best in a home with older children. He's okay with other cats as long as he has slow intros. He had teary eyes which a normal for him.
